videos.description: Alabama defeats Texas A&M 27-19, extending to a 20-game win streak in the SEC. Damien Harris powered his way for 124 yards and a touchdown to lead the Crimson Tide.
videos.title: College Football: Alabama defeats Texas A&M

videos.description: Michigan State takes down Michigan in the big house with a 14-10 upset victory. In a rainy game, the Spartan defense contributed 5 turnovers to take back the Paul Bunyan Trophy.
videos.title: College Football: Michigan State takes down Michigan

videos.description: Washington State moves to 6-0 for the first time since 2001 after defeating Oregon, 33-10. Luke Falk led the Cougars with 282 passing yards and 3 touchdowns.
videos.title: College Football: Washington State beats Oregon

videos.description: Wisconsin takes care of the Cornhuskers in Lincoln with a 38-17 victory. Wisconsin running back, Jonathan Taylor led the Badgers with 249 rushing yards and 2 touchdowns.
videos.title: College Football: Wisconsin beats Nebraska
